  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. The model is intended to predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed across all 13 credibility factors; seven factors were formally assessed and six were flagged as epistemic gaps. All assessed factors achieved required levels under MRL 5 constraints. Decision: Accepted. NOTE: Intended-use scope is described in the Claim and Requirement prose; no structured hasContextOfUse node is linked from this UnitOfAssurance.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-class3",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/cfd-hemolysis-vad-absolute-prediction",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/cfd-centrifugal-pump-hemolysis-v2",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-pump-piv-measurements",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-pump-hemolysis-bench"
  ],
